%% Sente Rails - Figure 6: Vertical 3 workflow - Cross-MDA business registration
%% Reference workflow 3 — cross-MDA business registration
%% "30 minutes from idea to formalised business" - clock visible on screen
%% Render: mmdc -i 06-workflow-vertical-3-cross-mda.mmd -o 06-workflow-vertical-3-cross-mda.svg -b transparent

sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Clerk as Counter Clerk<br/>(URSB / one-stop kiosk)
  participant Rail as Sente Rails<br/>/clerk + /v1
  participant MoMo as MTN MoMo<br/>(sandbox)
  participant URSB as URSB<br/>(Mode A surface)
  participant URA as URA<br/>(Mode B surface)
  participant Gulu as Gulu City Authority<br/>(Mode A surface)
  actor Citizen as Mukasa J. P.<br/>(prospective director)
  participant Supervisor as Supervisor screen<br/>(projected, optional)

  Note over Clerk,Citizen: Stage clock starts<br/>target: under 30 minutes end-to-end

  Clerk->>Rail: Search NIN CM78001234ABCD
  Rail-->>Clerk: Mukasa - verified

  Note over Clerk,Rail: Build cross-MDA cart
  Clerk->>Rail: Add NAME-RESERVE (URSB - 50,000)
  Clerk->>Rail: Add COMPANY-REG (URSB - 250,000)
  Clerk->>Rail: Add TIN-REG (URA - 0)
  Clerk->>Rail: Add TL-NEW (Gulu - 50,000)

  Rail-->>Clerk: Cross-MDA banner<br/>3 MDAs - 4 lines - 350,000 UGX

  Clerk->>Rail: Assess
  Rail->>Rail: FDN per efris_taxable line
  Rail-->>Clerk: Single assessment - 4 FDNs attached

  Clerk->>Rail: Pay via MoMo (single request)
  Rail->>MoMo: requestToPay 350,000 UGX
  MoMo-->>Citizen: USSD prompt
  Citizen-->>MoMo: PIN + approve

  MoMo-->>Rail: Webhook - SUCCESSFUL
  Rail->>MoMo: Split disbursement<br/>URSB: 300,000 - URA: 0 - Gulu: 50,000

  par Cross-MDA propagation in parallel
    Rail->>URSB: Webhook - issue Name + Company registration
    URSB-->>Rail: certificate refs - back-stamped on the assessment
  and
    Rail->>URA: Webhook - issue TIN
    URA-->>Rail: TIN number - back-stamped
  and
    Rail->>Gulu: Webhook - issue new trading licence
    Gulu-->>Rail: licence ref - back-stamped
  end

  Rail-->>Clerk: 3 receipts - one transaction - one citizen interaction

  opt Supervisor projection
    Rail->>Supervisor: Live shift tile updates<br/>(GULU + URSB + URA registers tick)
  end

  Note over Clerk,Citizen: Elapsed time<br/>contrast with current state (multi-day, multi-office)
